snippet.title: Sega Flash Vol. 7 - Enemy Zero Trailer
snippet.description:
Promo video for Enemy Zero on the Sega Saturn from Sega Flash Vol. 7.

The movie has a file date of 16th August 1996. The original resolution is 288x144, which is why it looks a bit blocky in the playback. I haven't re-encoded this, it's straight from the Truemotion AVI on the disc.
